
Storyline:

. admin logins
. while users login
  DONE - add them to default room
  DONE - display users connected in users browser
  DONE - display rooms in admin page
. admin clicks change state to "groups" (she wants to group people)
  DONE - admin clicks
  DONE - admin's client code sends event to server
  DONE - server creates the rooms
  DONE - server broadcasts the groups/rooms
  DONE - user code: update list (print you are in group mode)
  DONE - admin code: update room list

  - user code:
    - send audio/video to members of group
    - receive audio/video from others

